formThreeIdData.notesToCertificate:
1. The actual cost incurred for construction as per the books of accounts has been taken from unaudited books of accounts as on 20.06.2024 as certified by the management and relied upon by us. 
2. Total Estimated Cost of the Real Estate Project (1 (i) + 1 (ii) of Estimated Column have been taken on the basis of estimates made by the management
3. As per the documents produced before us and as explained by the management, total interest cost incurred was for the project on the loan taken for Rs 35 crore from ICICI Home Finance Company limited. 
4. In some of the cases, instead of executing agreement for sale, the promoter has executed sale deed in favor of customer. In those cases we have taken date of execution of sale deed as date of agreement for sale. 
5. We have taken and accepted the details of allotees such as KYC and Mobile number and not verified by us.
6. As per the Building Usage approved plane, the competent authority has provided BU permission for Block A+B+D except for the 716.51 sq mt built up area. The competent authority will give BU permission for the balance area i.e. (716.51 sq.mt) on being fulfilling the required condition as mentioned in the approved plan.
